ult' ><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-1\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/empd-application-forms\/#EMPD_Application_Forms_2024\" title=\"EMPD Application Forms 2024\">EMPD Application Forms 2024<\/a><\/li><li class='ez-toc-page-1 ez-toc-heading-level-2'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-2\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/empd-application-forms\/#Summary_of_the_Internship_Programme\" title=\"Summary of the Internship Programme:\">Summary of the Internship Programme:<\/a><ul class='ez-toc-list-level-3' ><li class='ez-toc-heading-level-3'><a class=\"ez-toc-link ez-toc-heading-3\" href=\"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/empd-application-forms\/#How_to_Apply_for_EMPD_Vacancies\" title=\"How to Apply for EMPD Vacancies\">How to Apply for EMPD Vacancies<\/a><\/li><\/ul><\/li><\/ul><\/nav><\/div>\n\n<p>The Ekurhuleni Metropolitan Police Department (EMPD) provide community safety, traffic policing and related security services and personal protection of the community, political offices, Council and visiting dignitaries.<\/p>\n<h2 id=\"empd-application-forms-2024\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"EMPD_Application_Forms_2024\"><\/span><span id=\"EMPD_Application_Forms_2024\">EMPD Application Forms 2024<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p>Looking for a career opportunity in the City of Ekurhuleni! Well, the opportunity within is just a click away.<\/p>\n<div class=\"contentlabelpanel\"><span id=\"requisitionListInterface.ID2266\" class=\"helplabel\">Take a few minutes to create or modify your employment profile and to specify your preferred working criteria for future openings matching your interests.<\/span><\/div>\n<h2 id=\"summary-of-the-internship-programme\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"Summary_of_the_Internship_Programme\"><\/span>Summary of the Internship Programme:<span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h2>\n<p><strong>POSITION(S):<\/strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 Several<\/p>\n<p><strong>COMPANY NAME:<\/strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Ekurhuleni Metropolitan Police Department (EMPD<\/p>\n<p><strong>VACANCY TYPE:<\/strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0Permanent\/Temporary.<\/p>\n<p><strong>CLOSING DATE:<\/strong>\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 not specified<\/p>\n<p><strong>REQUIREMENTS<\/strong><\/p>\n<p>Whether you are a school leaver, professional or tradesperson, EMPD could have a position to suit you. The City of Ekurhuleni aims to be an employer of choice by attracting highly-skilled people who will add value to the organisation.<\/p>\n<h3 id=\"how-to-apply-for-empd-vacancies\"><span class=\"ez-toc-section\" id=\"How_to_Apply_for_EMPD_Vacancies\"><\/span><span id=\"How_to_Apply_for_EMPD_Vacancies\">How to Apply for EMPD Vacancies<\/span><span class=\"ez-toc-section-end\"><\/span><\/h3>\n<section id=\"sp-main-body\">The Application Form for Employment at Ekurhuleni Metropolitan Police Department, EMPD is available for PDF download below;<\/section>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https:\/\/www.ekurhuleni.gov.za\/residents\/forms\/3706-om-115-application-form-for-employment-ekurhuleni-metropolitan-municipality-2\/file.html\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CLICK HERE TO APPLY.<\/a><\/strong><\/p>\n<p>&nbsp;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"The EMPD invite suitably qualified unemployed youth who meet the following requirements to apply for several outline positions&hellip;\n","protected":false},"author":1,"featured_media":3475,"comment_status":"closed","ping_status":"closed","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":{"footnotes":""},"categories":[12],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/3466"}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/applyjobs.org.ng\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/ty